Document Object Model is nothing but the description of the code in a visual way that is easy to understand .
It is like an ER Diagram model.
It gives the top or outer element of the tag and each tag that is present inside the tag is present below like a diagram.
It represents the HTML document as a tree structure.
DOM is a interface or an API used with programming language.DOM makes it easier to update read and access the data.
There are functions in DOM to do certain functions.
 
